snippet.title: Version 1.2 Teaser - "Tour de Inferno" | Zenless Zone Zero
snippet.description:
Listen up fuel-fiends, a new round of the Tour de Inferno is almost upon us!
The brave Biker Gangs are geared up and raring to go, and will soon compete to find out who's the strongest in the Hollows!
Who will emerge as the undisputed Overlord of the Old Oil Field?
Welcome to the Outer Ring. May you rise from the ashes!

—Welcome to New Eridu!—
PS5™/iOS/Android/PC | Version 1.1 "Undercover R&B" of Zenless Zone Zero, HoYoverse's urban fantasy ARPG, is out now: https://hoyo.link/5DbjFDAL.
